===Pronunciation===
מלוּכה / melûkâh / mel-oo-kaw'

===Etymology===
Feminine passive participle of {{HH|4427}}; 

===Noun===
'''מלוּכה'''

# Something ruled, that is, a realm: - [[kingdom]], king’s, X royal.

